{"tid":2223674,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ELISA告發經紀人性騷擾","createTime":"2020-09-30T04:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T09:49:05.000Z","uid":7307,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"27d4372dd2918b8460557b9633594c9ac29ed944","tid":2223674,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/18978192/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.livedoor.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F18978192%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=3171295d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.livedoor.com/article/detail/18978192/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcScOb1rZkG8kR9vpoCV-yLIGOPbarboVlyyVw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcScOb1rZkG8kR9vpoCV-yLIGOPbarboVlyyVw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=0d1012a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經紀人是已經有老婆小孩的人<br />\n從2018年5月開始負責ELISA的經紀工作<br />\n反正就是忍一次性騷擾之後 開始變本加厲<br />\n包括去年4月坐飛機去夏威夷參加活動時<br />\n「昨年4月にライブイベントでハワイを訪れた際には、飛行機の座席でズボンを下ろして&ldquo;舐めてほしい&rdquo;、と。ハワイでの公演後も、ホテルの部屋でお酒を飲んだ勢いで性行為を求められ、断り切れず&hellip;&hellip;。<br />\n去年4月在夏威夷舉行演唱會時，在飛機座位上脫下褲子說&lsquo;希望你能舔我&rsquo;。在夏威夷演出後，在酒店的房間里喝了酒，還要求發生性行為，我無法拒絕。<br />\nそれ以降、歌の練習中にリハーサル室に入ってきてキスを強要されたり、下着のなかに手を突っ込まれたこともある。私が引っ越したことを知ると、彼は電化製品の取り付けを手伝いにきたはずが、ベッドに押し倒しました。私が抵抗しながら&ldquo;自分が何をしているか分かってるの？&rdquo;と声を荒らげても、&ldquo;俺は本気だよ&rdquo;と言うのみ。もう我慢の限界でした。昨年11月に社長と面談して、全てを打ち明けたんです」<br />\n此後，在練習歌曲的過程中，曾進入排練室被強迫接吻，還被把手伸進內衣內。一知道我搬家了，他應該是來幫我安裝電器的，但是他把我推倒了床上。我抵抗著說:「你知道自己在做什麼嗎?」，只是說「我是認真的」。已經是忍耐的極限了。去年11月，我和社長面談時，把一切都告訴了他。"},{"pid":"28b37c4f33a7d0bf5fe6411d4b2f674871cfbf50","tid":2223674,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"睇到扯左"},{"pid":"66279d00024758909e8a5c2621222e5dbb2a7791","tid":2223674,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee6f0766e210e9df7de8454b2ee5481ca235a548","tid":2223674,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Elisa_%40_SakuraCon_%2714.jpg/1200px-Elisa_%40_SakuraCon_%2714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F1%2F1e%2FElisa_%2540_SakuraCon_%252714.jpg%2F1200px-Elisa_%2540_SakuraCon_%252714.jpg&h=f40edd45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41664076ce3274b99357fac36d7ba7c917017157","tid":2223674,"uid":106290,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"我無法拒絕<br />\n即係屌咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a151e3c923b068e9b80e664854fc2836eaf00b3","tid":2223674,"uid":34383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"屌左？ 唔至性擾擾咁簡單"},{"pid":"79f33c7611deed6fd29649152a5a27e275d9cf5a","tid":2223674,"uid":22590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"AV情節 = 結果社長都上埋一份..."},{"pid":"55bb434af4f68b26dede50a0eb7101d19f1e1e2d","tid":2223674,"uid":522,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"在夏威夷演出後，在酒店的房間里喝了酒，還要求發生性行為，我無法拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5524e8939b18c4ee2588dac825293b9cce3064","tid":2223674,"uid":38705,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"唔係想 blame the victim<br />\n但就咁睇呢兩段嘢<br />\n都講咗性關係維持咗半年<br />\n重要唔止扑過一次嘢<br />\n呢啲咁大件事,可以令個經理人即時收皮嘅事值得忍咁耐先講咩?"},{"pid":"087d50c724af8171552edb14b1f3587045e17086","tid":2223674,"uid":152542,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"断り切れず<br />\n竟然比經理人屌過<br />\n做經理人福利真係好 <br />\n西野加奈 又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa